'''Kuure Afahyɛ''' yɛ [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Zaare ɛwɔ Atifi Apuei Mantam wɔ Ghana no di, wɔn mu dodoɔ no ara yɛ atomfo. Wodi afahyɛ no wɔ bosome a edikan ne nea ɛtɔ so mienu no mu<ref>https://www.fiandadghanalimited.com/kuure-festival/</ref><ref>https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Woyi apayɛ na wɔ de twenebɔ ne asa toa so wɔ afahyɛ bere no mu<ref>http://h2829516.stratoserver.net/tourism/index.html</ref><ref>https://flygoldstar.com/tour-packages-uppereast-region.html</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi afahyɛ de yɛ nsɛnkyerɛne a egyina ho ma ‘’Kuure” a ɛne Asɔ wɔ Gurune kasa mu. Asɔ yɛ ade itiriw a, wɔde yɛ kua wɔ wɔn mpɔtam hɔ<ref>https://www.hugedomains.com/domain_profile.cfm?d=ghanaculturepolitics&e=com</ref><ref>https://ghananation.com/tourism/The-Upper-East-Region.php</ref>.

